/*

Purpose:			

Parameters:			

Return Value:		

Date		Who		Reason
15 June 2021	navndl1	Initial creation	TFS 51243 - post demo request from Bish.
											If started from menu, don't close just clear the fields ready for another.

*/

vars

begin

	self.myOutputTrackedItem := null;
